{"sequence":35,"timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:13:56.210322881Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-059e43c0","body":"Align `FindingClassification`’s serialized discriminator with the documented schema. `src/contexts/workflow_composition/review_classification.rs:50` uses `rename_all = \"snake_case\"`, and `src/contexts/workflow_composition/review_classification.rs:320-331` asserts `fix_now` / `planned_elsewhere` / `propose_new_bead`, but the bead spec defines the three classes as `fix-now`, `planned-elsewhere`, and `propose-new-bead` in `prompt-9ni721.md:13-23`. As written, persisted JSON using the documented labels will fail to deserialize, and this type will emit the wrong wire values for downstream prompt/rendering work.","dedup_key":"fb50bc8e6364d270cb95dc38001eeabf01110f9193f3a5888373e3708633b0ed","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260409194344","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":36,"timestamp":"2026-04-09T20:13:56.220181397Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-2-34d512f1","body":"Tighten `mapped_to_bead_id` syntax validation so obviously malformed IDs are rejected. `validate_bead_id_syntax` in `src/contexts/workflow_composition/review_classification.rs:88-108` currently allows values like `9ni.` or `bead.` because it only checks emptiness, whitespace, leading dot, and path separators. Elsewhere the codebase already treats an empty suffix after the milestone prefix as invalid (`src/contexts/milestone_record/bundle.rs:567-570`), and `strip_milestone_prefix` also rejects empty short IDs (`src/contexts/project_run_record/task_prompt_contract.rs:322-329`). That means `validate_classification` does not actually enforce the promised “syntactically valid” rule for `mapped_to_bead_id`.","dedup_key":"00a4d246fdcb665d2191ddda804fa1047e300ab9436831e5e68159609b586c95","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260409194344","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
